Job Description
To support the Demand Management process for Climate MEA products, timely and accurate forecast sent to all plants globally. Assist with sales and marketing analysis for the management team.
•             Co-ordinate with Sales managers and update forecasts on a monthly basis for all products
•             Participate in the S&OP and provide inputs to the demand management teams of the various plants
•             Update monthly numbers that needs to be reported to management based on inputs from MBRs and MEBMs
•             Support management team with Power Point charts for various business reviews/Management meetings
•             Analyze market information and update the sales organization/ management team with market trends.
•             Support marketing/sales organization with inputs required to develop management reports
•             Willing to take on additional marketing responsibilities to support the growth of the organization
Job Requirements
Strong analysis skills
Marketing background
3-5 years experience in a similar company with similar products
Currently based in the UAE